snippet: Al Horford scored 26 points and blocked six shots, Isaiah Thomas scored 14 of his 20 points in the second half and the Boston Celtics held off the Sacramento Kings 97-92 on Friday night....
lead_paragraph: Al Horford scored 26 points and blocked six shots, Isaiah Thomas scored 14 of his 20 points in the second half and the Boston Celtics held off the Sacramento Kings 97-92 on Friday night.

headline.main: Al Horford Scores 26 to Lead Celtics Over Kings 97-92
headline.print_headline: Al Horford Scores 26 to Lead Celtics Over Kings 97-92
